&lt;style&gt;
/ .. and write CSS accordingly /
.logged #login-box { display: none; }
&lt;/style&gt;	
</pre>

### CSS3 Feature Detection

<pre>
/ target CSS for browsers without box-shadow support /
.no-boxshadow .box {
   border: 2px solid #ddd;
}
</pre>

内置的检测项目如下：

- borderimage
